Watch your step around the big vent!

A fun map that makes humans work together for a once.

Map Includes:
-3 main holdouts

-teleport
-falling traps
-Crushing doors
-Water Trap

Added Lights! (If this version lags the server try the non lit version 4)
Added HDR support

=v4=
Reworked sewer area and changed out doors
Added water trap to sewer
Added lights to inform players when buttons are active again
Added more objects to the main 4 door holdout
Fixed glitchy elevator, now can't be blocked by players
Added new hiding spot in the lower area
Added falling trap to lower area
Fixed teleport and helped prevent players getting stuck when teleported

=v3=
Added 2 more blockage rooms
Added a ladder to the elevator shaft
48 spawns now
Removed the starting explosive barrels by spawn
Sewer gate opens out instead of in now
Added 2 more elevated catawalks
More boxes in the 4 door room
Shorter teleport restart time

=v2=

Fixed only having two spawn points (now 40)
Made level more fun for humans :]

Enjoy and happy zombie hunting.

An edit of d2_prison_02 map from HL2 for zombie mod. Includes barricade, holdout and jump spots. Don't change the content of the map without my knowledge. If you want some changes to the map ask me and I will do it.


Process of thought: I wanted some small map with limited number of reliable spots in order to force teamplay and have more zombies and more action. I also wanted the map to be some kind of underground but I couldn't decide on how to start. So I used one of HL2 maps as the base. To keep the map small i restricted myself to part of the original map. Eventually I saw some potential in the rest of map so I decide not to delete it. However, the full map will only be available randomly.

Have fun.

if you use this map on your server please contact me, so I can show you how stuff works + do changes to map if necessary. I can also help in testing your ZOMBIE MOD and ZOMBIE ESCAPE maps

After making (and failing) at actually "finishing" a map, this is the first. Took me around 3 days with a few hours out of each to finally complete.. There are some easter eggs in the map to be found.

- Party Room
- Teleport room
- Maze room
- 'Fall to your death' room
- 2 "Hidden" spots on the walls in the main room (Camping)

Teleports to these rooms are hidden underneath the midding building, underneath the slanted walkway things.. They are under those on the sides where the sofa's are. (One on each side.)

Teleports 1, 2, 3 Consist of 
1: Takes you back to the spawn point of the map
2: Takes you to the maze
3: Takes you to the 'Fall to your death' room.

Party room and the maze have teleports out of the rooms.. 'Fall to your death' room however doesn't. ('Cause you die, ya?)

The hidden spots are viewable by the shadows on the ground and walls. One is near the spawn point house (you need to get on top of the house to get on it) and the second is near the texture boxes at the north end of the map.

If you have any comments, suggestions for this or future maps, or any problems/bugs in the map tell me.

This map consists of four rooms.  There is a main room consisting of two houses and two climbing areas.  Both houses contain secrets.  On opposite ends of the main room there is a red tunnel, and a blue tunnel.  Each tunnel leads to one of the spawns, which consists of a small shack.

The final room is through a green tunnel from the main room, behind one of the climbing areas.  This is a model of a house I actually lived in.  There are also a few secrets in the house, as well as two pathways that lead to the attic.  The map was originally dark, but I've changed the lighting on it.

This map should be pretty decently balanced.  It is currently in the map rotation of the .zH. clan server.  If you'd like to check it out, visit 206.123.125.38:27016 and ask an admin to switch to that map.
